        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>12 Upper Gower St<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>.</placeName>
                    <date>Saturday Evening</date>
                    <salute>Dear Babbage</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                   
<p>I am exceedingly sorry that I troubled you unnecessarily for an extension of your kind invitation, as I happen to be so unwell to day, that I am quite unable to come.—</p>
<p>Pray excuse me having troubled you &amp; believe me Yours very truly | Chas. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        
    
        
